$pearl_page_construction["our-core-values"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="982"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="right_column" offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1429773153319{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-uniE6A3" style="style_3" icon_size="34" h_divider="true" title="INTEGRITY"]A tradition of ethical and honest business conduct is the cornerstone of our business philosophy, and the foundation of our entire organization.[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-uniE6A6" style="style_3" icon_size="28" h_divider="true" title="VISION"]We clearly identify our clients’ goals and visualize innovative solutions, using careful planning and proactive communication to achieve unparalleled results.[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1429773159549{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-uniE696" style="style_3" icon_size="39" h_divider="true" title="STAFF"]Our people is our success by delivering customer solutions. Therefore we strive continually to attract and retain talented professionals who share our values.[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-uniE6A7" style="style_3" icon_size="39" h_divider="true" title="SAFETY"]We focus on consistently upholding the highest standards of safety, ensuring that all workers and the public go home each and every day.[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1429773159549{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-uniE6A5" style="style_3" icon_size="37" h_divider="true" title="QUALITY"]We provide outstanding service through teamwork, experience, accountability and innovation – all of which is reflected 