$pearl_page_construction["careers"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="982"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="right_column" offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][vc_custom_heading text="BENEFITS AND REWARDS" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]Our people bring their technical knowledge, experience, and resourcefulness to the delivery of our construction services. As the largest general contractor in the country, BestBuild is a leader in all major market segments, including healthcare, education, commercial, sports, aviation, pharmaceutical, retail and green building. Driven by a commitment to continuous improvement, BestBuild embraces Building Information Modeling and lean construction methods to improve efficiency and enhance client value.[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion c_icon="triangle" active_section="1" autoplay="5" style="" shape="" color="" spacing="" gap="" c_align="" c_position="" css=".vc_custom_1490675647650{margin-bottom: 39px !important;}"][vc_tta_section title="Corporate Health and Wellness" tab_id="1490617357592-03169659-0e69"][vc_column_text]We recognize our primary asset is people. To be successful, BestBuild must be a rewarding place to work. We provide opportunity and encouragement to help our people reach their potential. Mutual respect provides the foundation for our success[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="our Company-Paid Benefits" tab_id="1490617357634-7e87b5b9-5435"][vc_column_text]BestBuild is interested in candidates with backgrounds related to construction management or engineering. But, like any other company, we are also looking for individuals in fields like finance, accounting, human resources and business development.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Training and Career Development" tab_id="1490617423595-a7ae1492-64d5"][vc_column_text]We are proactive in finding solutions for our clients that best achieve their goals. We understand that lasting relationships are the lifeblood of our business so we pay personal attention to our clients by focusing on them as individuals. Our founder referred to our clients, appropriately, as our “respected friends.”[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Pride in Working With Us" tab_id="1490617428207-db35e79e-76fa"][vc_column_text]On projects that develop and maintain a Lean culture of continuous improvement, our project teams have experienced improvements in design team and trade contractor relationships, communication, scope definition, coordination, cost and schedule performance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_custom_heading text="OPEN POSITIONS" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1490687048510{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][stm_vacancies text="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1431669852826{margin-bottom: -60px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3"][vc_column][stm_cta button_color="white" button_icon_pos="right" button_icon="fa fa-chevron-right" css_animation="bottom-to-top" align="" foo="My super title" link="url:%23quote|title:Get%20a%20quote||" css=".vc_custom_1490686969422{margin-bottom: 0px !important;background: #25da61 url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/bestbuild/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/03/stroke.png?id=41) !important;background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: repeat !important;}"] <h4 class="no_line"><span style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;">Looking for a quality and affordable constructor for your next project?</span></h4> [/stm_cta][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 1 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 2 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 3 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 4 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 5 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_wp_page_template' => arra