$pearl_page_construction["service-1"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text] <blockquote>Construction says that the better the service is delivered the higher is the skill level of our company. We work for the best quality of services for our clients and our clients appreciate us for that.</blockquote> [/vc_column_text][stm_carousel_gallery thumbnails="disable" description="disable" pagination="disable" images="1363,1364,1261,1260,1258,1263"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1491375308801{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1491375314289{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="SERVICE BROCHURE" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_single_image image="1365" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1491374924956{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column_text]As the general contractor, we first create the highest level of trust and integrity with our clients.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1491637388340{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="GENERAL CONTRACTING" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1491375060160{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1491375055696{margin-bottom: 12px !important;}"]Interior and spatial designers plan and organise the design of commercial and domestic interiors. Projects may take place in a range of settings, including:[/vc_column_text][stm_iconlist icon="fa fa-check" margins="13"] <ul> <li>office spaces and industrial premises;</li> <li>retail locations, such as shops, cafés, forecourts;</li> <li>leisure spaces, such as hotels, cinema foyers, holiday complexes;</li> <li>residential developments;</li> <li>domestic properties;</li> <li>ships and aircraft;</li> <li>public buildings, e.g. museums and civic buildings.</li> </ul> [/stm_iconlist][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion c_icon="triangle" active_section="1" css=".vc_custom_1491376092810{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_tta_section title="Sustainable Construction includes" tab_id="1491375722228-f872f8d7-6ad0"][vc_column_text]BestBuild says that the better the service is delivered the higher is the skill level of our company. We work for the best quality of services for our clients and our clients appreciate us for that.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="PERFORM VALUE ENGINEERING" tab_id="1491375721632-2be63b2e-f371"][vc_column_text]Beginning as early as possible in the life of a project, the Turner Engineering Group engages with Turner’s preconstruction and operations teams, as well as the project’s designer of record, to identify potential design and construction risks and opportunities to add value with engineered solutions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="INSPECTIONS AND OCCUPANCY PERMIT" tab_id="1491375720996-8adefa1e-9f32"][vc_column_text]On a design-build project, a Turner Engineering Group <strong>Design Manager</strong> provides insight, guidance, and leadership related to both the design itself, and the execution of that design — from the creation of project scope and contract agreements, through preconstruction and beyond.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="INSPECTIONS AND OCCUPANCY PERMIT" tab_id="1491375718993-369bb279-e707"][vc_column_text]Design Manages in turn engage the expertise of Turner Engineering Group <strong>Design Specialists</strong>, who bring advanced technical knowledge of individual disciplines, as the team determines the extent of the Turner Engineering Group’s involvement.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="PRECONSCTRUCTION SERVICES" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]Every construction is unique in scope, but process is systemically applied to each construction project. We seek to get involved early in the design phase so that we can manage the project more efficiently, provide effective building solutions, and identify challenges early on to mitigate design changes after construction commencement. This involves detailed pre-construction planning crucial to successful construction and on-time delivery, and allows the client and team a clear pathway to the bidding process, construction phase, and through to completion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="GENERAL CONTRACTING PROJECTS" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1491376148973{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][stm_projects_carousel style_carousel="style_2" img_size="400x230" number="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 1 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), '_wp_old_slug' => array ( 0 => 'service-test', 1 => 'sustainable-construction-2', ), '_dp_original' => array ( 0 => '1348', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1510209623:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_thumbnail_id' => array ( 0 => '1255', ), 'page_title_breadcrumbs' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_line_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1491375308801{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375314289{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1491637388340{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1491374924956{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375060160{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375055696{margin-bottom: 12px !important;}.vc_custom_1491376092810{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}.vc_custom_1491376148973{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h2', ), 'service_icon' => array ( 0 => 'stmicon-bon-house', ), 'service_price' => array ( 0 => '150$', ), 'service_badge' => array ( 0 => 'HOT', ), ), );
$pearl_page_construction["service-2"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1491375308801{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1491638403495{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="GENERAL CONTRACTING" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1491375060160{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1491375055696{margin-bottom: 12px !important;}"]Interior and spatial designers plan and organise the design of commercial and domestic interiors. Projects may take place in a range of settings, including:[/vc_column_text][stm_iconlist icon="fa fa-check" margins="13"] <ul> <li>office spaces and industrial premises;</li> <li>retail locations, such as shops, cafés, forecourts;</li> <li>leisure spaces, such as hotels, cinema foyers, holiday complexes;</li> <li>residential developments;</li> <li>domestic properties;</li> <li>ships and aircraft;</li> <li>public buildings, e.g. museums and civic buildings.</li> </ul> [/stm_iconlist][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1491375314289{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="SERVICE BROCHURE" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_single_image image="1365" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1491374924956{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column_text]As the general contractor, we first create the highest level of trust and integrity with our clients.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="PRECONSCTRUCTION SERVICES" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]Every construction is unique in scope, but process is systemically applied to each construction project. We seek to get involved early in the design phase so that we can manage the project more efficiently, provide effective building solutions, and identify challenges early on to mitigate design changes after construction commencement. This involves detailed pre-construction planning crucial to successful construction and on-time delivery, and allows the client and team a clear pathway to the bidding process, construction phase, and through to completion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="GENERAL CONTRACTING PROJECTS" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1491376148973{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][stm_projects_carousel style_carousel="style_2" img_size="400x230" number="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1491376912980{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}"] <blockquote>Construction says that the better the service is delivered the higher is the skill level of our company. We work for the best quality of services for our clients and our clients appreciate us for that.</blockquote> [/vc_column_text][stm_carousel_gallery thumbnails="disable" description="disable" pagination="disable" images="1363,1364,1261,1260,1258,1263"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion c_icon="triangle" active_section="1" css=".vc_custom_1491376092810{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_tta_section title="Sustainable Construction includes" tab_id="1491375722228-f872f8d7-6ad0"][vc_column_text]Construction says that the better the service is delivered the higher is the skill level of our company. We work for the best quality of services for our clients and our clients appreciate us for that.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="PERFORM VALUE ENGINEERING" tab_id="1491375721632-2be63b2e-f371"][vc_column_text]Stellar provides design-only services, or competitively bids and self-performs construction services. We work closely with contractors to ensure questions and issues are addressed prior to locking in the GMP, and can also provide owners with our recommendations on which contractor provides the most value.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="INSPECTIONS AND OCCUPANCY PERMIT" tab_id="1491375720996-8adefa1e-9f32"][vc_column_text]With cross-functional collaboration, we self-perform the project from design through closeout to provide a single source of accountability and greater efficiency. Because the design process is more fluid, we can proactively begin the construction process (including identifying and procuring long-lead items) before the design reaches 100 percent, delivering greater speed to market to our owners.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="INSPECTIONS AND OCCUPANCY PERMIT" tab_id="1491375718993-369bb279-e707"][vc_column_text]Our team’s EPCM experience includes both domestic and international projects, where our highly skilled construction project managers, technical architects and engineering leadership apply our extensive construction planning, scheduling and design expertise. We assume responsibility for everything from the site, building design, process design and purchase. Stellar also secures equipment in addition to overseeing and coordinating the client’s subcontracts or trade contracts.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1510209667:1', ), '_thumbnail_id' => array ( 0 => '1253', ), '_wp_old_slug' => array ( 0 => 'service-test', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1491375308801{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1491638403495{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375314289{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375060160{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}.vc_custom_1491375055696{margin-bottom: 12px !important;}.vc_custom_1491374924956{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}.vc_custom_14913761